{
 "name": "RPlog_Pirates_and_Pork",
 "title": "Pirates and Pork",
 "summary": "A motley boarding party of Maffi soldiers aboard a commandeered Corporate Sector Security ship descends on a pirate-held vessel, led by Gren Delede and his Twi'lek partner Twila, with the relentless war droid Zed in their fodder-friendly vanguard. In a series of brutal, gory firefights through corridors and the armoury, the team cuts down the unskilled pirates, Zed wading through blaster fire and glop grenades to leave melted, blood-soaked corpses in his wake. The fight grows desperate in the command center, where the pirate leader's axe-wielding Gamorrean guards nearly overwhelm Zed before the droid turns them against their masters and butchers the Twi'lek pirates. Bloodied and wounded, Gren and the limping Twila finish the job, ordering Zed to kill the last of the pork and get the injured to a medic.",
